issue.title: Merge NextJS rewrite
issue.body:
This was quite a bit of effort, but I think it was well worth it.

# New features
- Server-side search
- Interactive map
- New multi-step hospital import flow (this is _big_)
- Price stats
- IP based geolocation
- Lazy loading of nearby hospitals
- General stability and cleanliness improvements (_scoped CSS! wow!_)
